Ar sathe jodi thake tomar moto soi, 
Hoi hoi kore jagte pari, jagate pari thoi. 
 Odike, oi Dhaka Towerer opase jara thake 
Kothar fake boli shono, dhongta tader emon, 
Jeno monta ora bondho korei rakhe. 
 Amar abar raatri kiser? 
Sokal Dupur Shondha bolo, 
Bisher neshay pranta kemon 
Biran hoei thake... 
 Majhe moddhe, keu ki Tobe
Aamar kotha mone rakhe !!!
                            
